...and C. Banks, number 4317.

5
00:02:43,314 --> 00:02:46,683
'Ashes to ashes, dust to dust.'

6
00:02:48,069 --> 00:02:50,525
May God have mercy on their souls.

7
00:02:51,072 --> 00:02:52,899
- Amen.
- Amen.

8
00:02:53,908 --> 00:02:55,901
