a little colder.

1055
01:16:56,809 --> 01:16:58,433
I have a dream.

1056
01:17:00,480 --> 01:17:04,098
I'm the greatest! I'm the king of the world.

1057
01:17:17,455 --> 01:17:19,531
We got to fight for ourselves.

1058
01:17:32,428 --> 01:17:34,753
I'll see y'all in New York City!

1059
01:17:35,306 --> 01:17:36,848
Oh, shit!

1060
01:18:29,235 --> 01:18:30,943
Round about 1972...

1061
01:18:31,946 --> 01:18:34,022
...I got transferred to the infirmary...

1062
01:18:34,741 --> 01:18:37,314
...and those two fools were still at it.

1063
01:18:41,914 --> 01:18:44,286
But no matter how tough a man is...

1064
01:18:44,584 --> 01:18:46,790
...he spends enough time on this farm...

1065
01:18:46,877 --> 01:18:49,084
...he'll find his breaking point.

1066
01:18:49,672 --> 01:18:52,377
It could be triggered by any little thing.

1067
01:18:52,509 --> 01:18:54,797
A face. A voice. Even a smell.

1068
01:19:06,147 --> 01:19:07,724
White-only pies.

1069
01:19:12,278 --> 01:19:13,938
Man over the line!

1070
01:19:29,128 --> 01:19:30,872
That boy went crazy.

1071
01:19:36,094 --> 01:19:37,671
You comfortable?

1072
01:19:38,429 --> 01:19:41,181
As a pair of fur-lined bedroom slippers.

1073
01:19:43,059 --> 01:19:46,594
That's very amusin'.
We'll see how them slippers feel...

1074
01:19:46,979 --> 01:19:48,888
...after about 24 hours.

1075
01:19:52,193 --> 01:19:53,936
I need a volunteer!

1076
01:19:55,196 --> 01:19:56,821
Gibson, stand up.

1077
01:19:57,991 --> 01:20:00,316
I'll make you trusty right now.

1078
01:20:00,451 --> 01:20:03,120
If that pie-eatin' bastard step off
them bottles...

1079
01:20:03,204 --> 01:20:05,327
...if so much as one toe hit that dirt...

1080
01:20:05,415 --> 01:20:07,573
...I want you to shoot him in his ass.

1081
01:20:08,918 --> 01:20:12,252
I want you to kill him.
I want you to shoot him dead.

1082
01:20:12,714 --> 01:20:15,335
You do that, I swear to God,
you're a free man.

1083
01:20:15,425 --> 01:20:18,176
I'll walk you out the gate myself.

1084
01:20:18,803 --> 01:20:20,297
What d'ya say?

1085
01:20:24,684 --> 01:20:27,257
I got to be honest with you, boss.

1086
01:20:27,353 --> 01:20:31,398
You don't wanna give me that gun,
'cause I'd probably shoot you with it.

1087
01:20:33,610 --> 01:20:35,816
That was the wrong answer, boy.

1088
01:20:37,447 --> 01:20:40,068
You a fool. I'd have taken that deal.

1089
01:20:41,116 --> 01:20:43,738
I beg pardon? You say something to me?

1090
01:20:43,995 --> 01:20:46,782
I'd have knocked you off,
put a bullet in your ass...

1091
01:20:46,872 --> 01:20:49,198
...and be halfway to New York right now.

1092
01:20:51,043 --> 01:20:54,626
Well, my goodness.
After all these years of blissful silence...

1093
01:20:54,881 --> 01:20:58,048
...I forgot how annoying
the sound of your voice is.

1094
01:20:58,968 --> 01:21:02,882
I hope you know
I don't owe you a damn thing.

1095
01:21:02,972 --> 01:21:05,380
I ain't do nothin' for you to owe me.

1096
01:21:05,475 --> 01:21:08,262
What you got I ain't got? I did it for me.

1097
01:21:08,352 --> 01:21:11,971
I'm a man. I ain't no motherfucking,
bootlickin' trusty.

1098
01:21:12,148 --> 01:21:14,437
You'll make me fall off, talkin' to your ass.

1099
01:21:14,525 --> 01:21:17,526
It's about being poised.
Just poise yourself.

1100
01:21:17,820 --> 01:21:19,315
Poise, my ass.

1101
01:21:24,452 --> 01:21:27,121
Sorry to hear about your mama passing.

1102
01:21:28,957 --> 01:21:31,079
Yeah, about five years ago.

1103
01:21:31,250 --> 01:21:32,495
Thank you.

1104
01:21:33,294 --> 01:21:35,500
Since we're talkin', I thought I'd mention it.

1105
01:21:35,588 --> 01:21:39,039
We not talkin', you talkin'.
And doin' a little bit too much of it.

1106
01:21:39,133 --> 01:21:41,589
Every time you start talkin', I almost fall...

1107
01:21:41,678 --> 01:21:44,169
- Would you stop...
- Don't say nothin' else to me!

1108
01:21:44,263 --> 01:21:47,632
- You about to make me fall.
- Hold still, don't say nothin'.

1109
01:21:51,187 --> 01:21:53,891
Oh! Damn, one of my toes in the bottle.

1110
01:21:54,232 --> 01:21:55,975
Damn it, Ray, shit.

1111
01:22:04,617 --> 01:22:07,404
What you laughin' about?
What's so funny?

1112
01:22:10,039 --> 01:22:13,158
Thinkin' about you runnin' with bullets
flyin' over your head.

1113
01:22:13,251 --> 01:22:16,287
That's something to see there.
That was a sight to see.

1114
01:22:16,379 --> 01:22:18,502
Bullets weren't the problem, Ray.

1115
01:22:18,589 --> 01:22:20,381
That pie was too hot.

1116
01:22:20,716 --> 01:22:22,543
Burned my damn tongue.

1117
01:22:26,347 --> 01:22:29,182
It sure is good talkin' to you again.

1118
01:22:30,852 --> 01:22:32,845
Good talkin' to you too.

1119
01:22:34,689 --> 01:22:36,266
Come on! Let's move!

1120
01:22:36,357 --> 01:22:39,311
We got 14 acres of land to clear today!
Let's go!

1121
01:22:39,527 --> 01:22:42,528
Gibson, Banks,
get your sorry asses over here.

1122
01:22:45,283 --> 01:22:47,690
Every mornin' I wake up prayin'...

1123
01:22:48,619 --> 01:22:52,238
...that the two of you
have died in their sleep.

1124
01:22:52,957 --> 01:22:55,495
And every mornin' you disappoint me.

1125
01:22:56,002 --> 01:22:57,413
Sorry, boss.

1126
01:22:58,630 --> 01:23:01,749
You two got 15 minutes
to clear out your lockers.

1127
01:23:01,841 --> 01:23:05,886
The both of you have been transferred
to the superintendent's mansion.

1128
01:23:06,054 --> 01:23:08,379
And I, for one, won't miss you.

1129
01:23:20,109 --> 01:23:22,232
Here's your medicine, Mr. Wilkins.

1130
01:23:22,612 --> 01:23:24,735
My pills. Thank you.

1131
01:23:24,989 --> 01:23:26,483
You're welcome.

1132
01:23:35,500 --> 01:23:36,958
Oh, yard boy.

1133
01:23:38,211 --> 01:23:40,784
This myrtle could use some attention.

1134
01:23:40,922 --> 01:23:44,255
Perhaps some fertilizer
would restore its exuberance.

1135
01:23:46,761 --> 01:23:48,553
Get your ass to work.

1136
01:23:52,475 --> 01:23:55,049
Tell me what you think of this place.

1137
01:23:55,979 --> 01:23:59,014
