1139
01:24:01,984 --> 01:24:05,603
I ought to try to enjoy myself
what few years I got left.

1140
01:24:07,991 --> 01:24:09,948
Let's take a look at this.

1141
01:24:10,117 --> 01:24:13,617
Eyesight ain't what it once was.
Ooh, this is nice here.

1142
01:24:15,123 --> 01:24:18,990
'Ocean views... palm trees.'

1143
01:24:20,086 --> 01:24:22,078
'Two heated swimming pools.'

1144
01:24:22,922 --> 01:24:26,754
Sounds a damn sight better
than that infirmary across the way...

1145
01:24:26,843 --> 01:24:29,714
...where I'm gonna end up, I'll tell you that.

1146
01:24:37,061 --> 01:24:40,015
I must apologize. That was rude of me.

1147
01:24:40,982 --> 01:24:45,525
That's all right. Takes more than
some colorful brochure to hurt my feelings.

1148
01:24:47,280 --> 01:24:50,731
You've been on the farm for quite a spell,
haven't you?

1149
01:24:51,200 --> 01:24:54,285
Over 40 years now.
Me and Ray Gibson out there.

1150
01:24:55,204 --> 01:24:56,615
Forty years.

1151
01:24:57,748 --> 01:25:00,418
That's a long time for any crime,
even murder.

1152
01:25:01,127 --> 01:25:04,377
It's a hell of a lot longer
when you're innocent.

1153
01:25:05,340 --> 01:25:09,040
Half the men in this prison
swear they're innocent.

1154
01:25:10,219 --> 01:25:12,342
Don't ya think that's kinda funny?

1155
01:25:12,680 --> 01:25:15,385
You have to forgive me if I don't laugh.

1156
01:25:16,601 --> 01:25:17,929
Excuse me.

1157
01:25:28,238 --> 01:25:30,195
What you lookin' at, Ray?

1158
01:25:34,201 --> 01:25:37,903
- Just what the fuck you lookin' at?
- I noticed that...

1159
01:25:38,665 --> 01:25:41,998
...I noticed you and Mr. Wilkins
been mighty friendly lately.

1160
01:25:42,084 --> 01:25:44,208
Y'all wanna be a new couple or somethin'?

1161
01:25:44,295 --> 01:25:46,252
Kiss my ass.

1162
01:25:47,590 --> 01:25:50,046
Mr. Wilkins just an old man
that like to talk.

1163
01:25:50,135 --> 01:25:52,672
That's all that is, Ray. That's all.

1164
01:25:53,512 --> 01:25:56,882
Y'all like to talk.
I'm lonely, and I like to talk too.

1165
01:25:56,975 --> 01:25:59,133
What you wanna talk about?

1166
01:26:00,728 --> 01:26:03,349
I wanna talk about the plan
you've been working on.

1167
01:26:03,439 --> 01:26:05,432
I ain't workin' on no plan!

1168
01:26:05,650 --> 01:26:09,695
I know ya. And I know
when you got somethin' brewin'.

1169
01:26:10,738 --> 01:26:12,695
What I got brewin'?

1170
01:26:13,575 --> 01:26:16,529
- You tell me!
- You done lost your damn mind.

1171
01:26:18,079 --> 01:26:20,321
I don't care what you believe.

1172
01:26:20,498 --> 01:26:22,537
You got somethin' up your sleeve.

1173
01:26:22,625 --> 01:26:24,748
